        <body>
            <entry xml:id="entry_æǧnæg" xml:lang="os">
                <form xml:id="form_d3048e66" type="lemma"><orth>æǧnæg</orth></form>
                <sense xml:id="sense_d3048e69"><sense xml:id="sense_d3048e70"><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>застежка</q>
                        </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>clasp</q>
                        </abv:tr></sense><sense xml:id="sense_d3048e79"><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>пуговица</q>
                        </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>button</q>
                        </abv:tr></sense></sense>
                <abv:exampleGrp xml:id="exampleGrp_d3048e89">
                    <abv:example xml:id="example_d3048e91">
                        <quote>rīwy ʽǧnæǵytæ qazync st’alytaw</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>застежки на груди играют, как звезды</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>clasps on chest sparkle like stars</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Коста"/><biblScope>19</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                    <abv:example xml:id="example_d3048e110">
                        <quote>ængom cærūt, æǧnæg æmæ sæxtæg k˳yd cærync</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>живите дружно, как живут пуговица и петля</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>live together like a button and a buttonhole</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                    </abv:example>
                    <abv:example xml:id="example_d3048e125">
                        <quote>ūj bæsty wal dæ æǧnæǵytæ æværyn sax˳yr ū</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>лучше бы ты научился застегивать свои пуговицы</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>you'd better learn how to button up</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Брит."/><biblScope>42</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                </abv:exampleGrp>
                <etym xml:lang="ru">Восстанавливаем в <hi rendition="#rend_italic">*æx-mæg</hi>, <hi rendition="#rend_italic">*ærx-næg</hi>, где <hi rendition="#rend_italic">-næg</hi> —
                    суффиксальное (из <hi rendition="#rend_italic">-na</hi> + <hi rendition="#rend_italic">ka</hi>), как в <ref type="xr" target="#entry_xærnæg"/>, <ref type="xr" target="#entry_īwnæg"/>, <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ægæjnæg"/>, <ref type="xr" target="#entry_tawnæg"/> и др.
                    Элемент <hi rendition="#rend_italic">æx-</hi>, <hi rendition="#rend_italic">ærx-</hi> со значением ‘скрепление’, ‘скреплять’ и пр.
                        (<mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d3048e215" xml:id="mentioned_d3048e155" xml:lang="x-oldirn"><lang/>
                        <w>*ark-</w></mentioned>) мы находим еще в следующих словах: <ref type="xr" target="#entry_æxkænyn"/> ‘запирать’, <ref type="xr" target="#entry_æxtong"/> ‘подпруга’ и д. <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ærxu"/> ‘плотно замкнутый’,
                        <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ærxæg"/> | <hi rendition="#rend_italic">ærxængæ</hi> ‘сустав’, <ref type="xr" target="#entry_arx"/> ‘сук’ и, может быть, <ref type="xr" target="#entry_arkʼaw"/> ‘клещи’. Для семантического ряда ‘застежка’ — ‘сук’
                    — ‘клещи’ ср. <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d3048e234" xml:id="mentioned_d3048e174" xml:lang="fa"><lang/>
                        <w>giri</w>
                        <gloss><q>застежка</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d3048e242" xml:id="mentioned_d3048e182" xml:lang="fa"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>узел</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d3048e248" xml:id="mentioned_d3048e188" xml:lang="fa"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>сук</q></gloss></mentioned> и <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d3048e254" xml:id="mentioned_d3048e194" xml:lang="fa"><lang/>
                        <w>gīra</w>
                        <gloss><q>клещи</q></gloss></mentioned>. См. <ref type="xr" target="#entry_æxkænyn"/>.</etym>
                <etym xml:lang="en">We reconstruct it as <hi rendition="#rend_italic">*æx-mæg</hi>, <hi rendition="#rend_italic">*ærx-næg</hi>, where <hi rendition="#rend_italic">-næg</hi>
                    is a suffix (from <hi rendition="#rend_italic">-na</hi> + <hi rendition="#rend_italic">ka</hi>), like in <ref type="xr" target="#entry_xærnæg"/>, <ref type="xr" target="#entry_īwnæg"/>, <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ægæjnæg"/>, <ref type="xr" target="#entry_tawnæg"/>
                    etc. The element <hi rendition="#rend_italic">æx-</hi>, <hi rendition="#rend_italic">ærx-</hi> with the meaning ‘fastening’, ‘fasten’ etc.
                        (<mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d3048e155" xml:id="mentioned_d3048e215" xml:lang="x-oldirn"><lang/>
                        <w>*ark-</w></mentioned>) we can find in other words: <ref type="xr" target="#entry_æxkænyn"/> ‘lock’, <ref type="xr" target="#entry_æxtong"/>
                    ‘girth’ and Digor <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ærxu"/> ‘tightly closed’, <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ærxæg"/> | <hi rendition="#rend_italic">ærxængæ</hi> ‘joint’, <ref type="xr" target="#entry_arx"/> ‘bough’ and, perhaps, <ref type="xr" target="#entry_arkʼaw"/> ‘pliers’. For the semantic chain ‘clasp’ — ‘bough’
                    — ‘pliers’ cf. <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d3048e174" xml:id="mentioned_d3048e234" xml:lang="fa"><lang/>
                        <w>giri</w>
                        <gloss><q>clasp</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d3048e182" xml:id="mentioned_d3048e242" xml:lang="fa"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>knot</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d3048e188" xml:id="mentioned_d3048e248" xml:lang="fa"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>bough</q></gloss></mentioned> and <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d3048e194" xml:id="mentioned_d3048e254" xml:lang="fa"><lang/>
                        <w>gīra</w>
                        <gloss><q>pliers</q></gloss></mentioned>. Cf. <ref type="xr" target="#entry_æxkænyn"/>.</etym>
            </entry>
